title: Bug 23267[Import/Export] Import Project should have a default folder
description: Bug 23267[Import/Export] Import Project should have a default folder
OB: When importing an existing Eclipse project on XP and clicking the Browse button, the current behavior is that the import dialog does not have a default folder.
EB: It would be helpful if the import dialog had a default folder that remembers the last folder from which I imported a project.
